<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>néng chū yī bǎ lì jiù chū yī bǎ lì 迦南1027</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 néng chū yī bǎ lì jiù chū yī bǎ lì, néng diǎn rán yī gè huǒ bǎ jiù diǎn rán yī gè huǒ bǎ.
 yīn wèi wǒ men tóng xīn qù zuò lì liàng dà. fú yīn yī dìng chuán biàn zhōng huá.
 kàn nǎ bái gē fēi lái, kàn nǎ hé chǎng guǎng dà.
 qiān dòng wǒ men de shì xiàn, qián jìn de bù fá. zhōng xīn qù bǎ zhǔ ài bō sā.
 qǐ lái ba shén de ér nǚ, dōu yào jīng shòu fēng chuī yǔ dǎ.
 qián jìn ba shén de ér nǚ, shén bì fù xìng tā de jiā.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1027</hymn_number>
</song>